    <!-- Privacy Policy (stub — flag for real legal copy) -->
    <string name="privacy_policy_content">PLACEHOLDER — This privacy policy requires real legal copy before Play Store submission.\n\nFocus Shield collects the following data, all stored locally on your device:\n• App usage statistics (which monitored apps were opened and when)\n• Blocked content events (timestamp, app, content type)\n• Study session records\n• Focus streaks and achievement progress\n\nNo data leaves your device unless you explicitly enable cloud sync (v2 feature).\n\nFocus Shield uses the Accessibility Service solely for detecting short-form content surfaces within monitored apps. It does not read, store, or transmit your personal content, messages, passwords, or browsing history.\n\nContact: [your-email@example.com]</string>
